<p class="Titolo">Numbers</p>
<p class="Sottotitolo">Can you count to twenty?</p>
<span class="Testo">&nbsp;
																							  <meta content="text/html; charset=ISO-8859-1" http-equiv="content-type"><title>Numbers</title><meta http-equiv="CONTENT-TYPE" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><title></title><meta name="GENERATOR" content="LibreOffice 3.5  (Linux)"><style type="text/css"><!--		@page { margin: 2cm }		P { margin-bottom: 0.21cm; direction: ltr; color: #000000; widows: 2; orphans: 2 }		A:link { color: #0000ff; so-language: zxx }	--></style><h3 style="color: rgb(0, 0, 153);"><font face="Trebuchet MS, serif"><font size="4"><b><span style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">COUNTAND MOVE</span></b></font></font></h3><font style="font-family: Verdana; color: rgb(0, 0, 153);" face="Trebuchet MS, serif">Ecco avoi una canzone divertente e movimentata: la marcia dei numeri.Attraverso questo video i vostri bambini impareranno a contare fino aventi divertendosi a pronunciare il numero contemporaneamente allavoce principale e, per i numeri che ancora non conoscono, silasceranno guidare dalla canzone!</font><span style="font-family: Verdana; color: rgb(0, 0, 153);"><br></span><font style="font-family: Verdana; color: rgb(0, 0, 153);" face="Trebuchet MS, serif">E non dimenticatevi,&nbsp; è una marcia dei numeri quindi ... ci simuove mentre la si canta !<br></font><meta http-equiv="CONTENT-TYPE" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><title></title><meta name="GENERATOR" content="LibreOffice 3.5  (Linux)"><style type="text/css"><!--		@page { margin: 2cm }		P { margin-bottom: 0.21cm; direction: ltr; color: #000000; widows: 2; orphans: 2 }		A:link { color: #0000ff; so-language: zxx }	--></style><p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><font face="Trebuchet MS, serif"><b>LINK</b></font></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><font color="#0000ff"><span lang="zxx"><u><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Aq4UAss33qA"><font face="Trebuchet MS,serif"><b>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Aq4UAss33qA</b></font></a></u></span></font></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><br></p><br><iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/ShqXL-zfLxY?rel=0" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="315" width="540"></iframe><br><font style="font-family: Verdana; color: rgb(0, 0, 153);" face="Trebuchet MS, serif"><br></font><meta http-equiv="CONTENT-TYPE" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><title></title><meta name="GENERATOR" content="LibreOffice 3.5  (Linux)"><style type="text/css"><!--		@page { margin: 2cm }		P { margin-bottom: 0.21cm; direction: ltr; color: #000000; widows: 2; orphans: 2 }		A:link { color: #0000ff; so-language: zxx }	--></style><h3 style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102);"><span lang="en-US"><b>testodella canzone<br></b></span></h3><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102);"><em><font style="font-size: 9pt;" size="2">Let's get started with some counting!</font></em><font style="font-size: 9pt;" size="2"></font><em><font style="font-size: 9pt;" size="2"> Can you count to 20?</font></em><font style="font-size: 9pt;" size="2">&nbsp;</font><font style="font-size: 9pt;" size="2"><br></font><em><font style="font-size: 9pt;" size="2">Here we go!</font></em><font style="font-size: 9pt;" size="2"></font><font style="font-size: 9pt;" size="2"> One! Two! Three! Four! Five! Six! Seven! Eight! Nine! Ten!Eleven! Twelve! Thirteen. Fourteen. Fifteen. Sixteen. Seventeen!Eighteen! Nineteen! Twenty!</font><font style="font-size: 9pt;" size="2"><span lang="it-IT">YAY!!!!!!</span></font><font style="font-size: 9pt;" size="2"><span lang="it-IT">&nbsp;</span></font><font style="font-size: 9pt;" size="2"><span lang="it-IT"></span></font><em><font style="font-size: 9pt;" size="2"><span lang="it-IT">That was fun!</span></font></em><font style="font-size: 9pt;" size="2"><span lang="it-IT">&nbsp;</span></font></p><br><br><br><meta content="text/html; charset=ISO-8859-1" http-equiv="content-type"><title>Numbers</title><meta http-equiv="CONTENT-TYPE" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><title></title><meta name="GENERATOR" content="LibreOffice 3.5  (Linux)"><style type="text/css"><!--		@page { margin: 2cm }		P { margin-bottom: 0.21cm; direction: ltr; color: #000000; widows: 2; orphans: 2 }		A:link { color: #0000ff; so-language: zxx }	--></style><h3 style="color: rgb(0, 0, 153);"><font face="Trebuchet MS, serif"><font size="4"><b><span style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">HOW MANY<br></span></b></font></font></h3><font style="font-family: Verdana; color: rgb(0, 0, 153);" face="Trebuchet MS, serif">Con questa canzone i bambini, oltre arafforzare la conoscenza dei numeri fino al dieci, inizieranno aprender confidenza con la domanda “How many?”. Verrà poi naturale chevi chiedano il significato di queste parole e allora, da una lorocuriosità, potrete iniziare a giocare (come facevamo in classe) algioco dell’<span style="font-weight: bold;"> “ How many?”</span> : Howmany boys are here? How many teacher are here? How many girls with longhair are here?Non importa se in questo gioco utilizzerete termini che i bambini nonconoscono, poiché potete aiutarli indicando o suggerendosuccessivamente il termine in lingua italiana sempre seguito poi daquello inglese. Per esempio : girate per la casa con aria pensierosadicendo “How many… How many.. How many…How many apples are in thefridge?” E aprendo il frigo indicate le mele e magari iniziate acontarle insieme al bambino; oppure How many… how many… how many… chairare in the kitchen? E mentre si dice la parola chair si indica la sediamentre, dicendo la parola kitchen si dice sottovoce cucina e poi siripete nuovamente l’intera domanda così da permettere al bambino dimemorizzare il significato delle parole.Chi si appresta ad imparare la lingua inglese trova spesso difficoltà acapire quando usare How many e quando How much; con questa canzone esoprattutto con il gioco che segue i vostri bambini imparerannonaturalmente che How many si usa quando si vuole domandare una quantitàche può essere rappresentata con un numero…il resto lo apprenderanno inseguito!</font><meta http-equiv="CONTENT-TYPE" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><title></title><meta name="GENERATOR" content="LibreOffice 3.5  (Linux)"><style type="text/css"><!--		@page { margin: 2cm }		P { margin-bottom: 0.21cm; direction: ltr; color: #000000; widows: 2; orphans: 2 }		A:link { color: #0000ff; so-language: zxx }	--></style><meta http-equiv="CONTENT-TYPE" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><title></title><meta name="GENERATOR" content="LibreOffice 3.5  (Linux)"><style type="text/css"><!--		@page { margin: 2cm }		P { margin-bottom: 0.21cm; direction: ltr; color: #000000; widows: 2; orphans: 2 }		A:link { color: #0000ff; so-language: zxx }	--></style><p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><font face="Trebuchet MS, serif"><b>LINK</b></font></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><font color="#0000ff"><span lang="zxx"><u><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G3zaC5onBvM"><font face="Trebuchet MS,serif"><b>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G3zaC5onBvM</b></font></a></u></span></font></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><br></p><br><iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/G3zaC5onBvM?rel=0" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="315" width="540"></iframe><br><font style="font-family: Verdana; color: rgb(0, 0, 153);" face="Trebuchet MS, serif"><br></font><meta http-equiv="CONTENT-TYPE" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><title></title><meta name="GENERATOR" content="LibreOffice 3.5  (Linux)"><style type="text/css"><!--		@page { margin: 2cm }		P { margin-bottom: 0.21cm; direction: ltr; color: #000000; widows: 2; orphans: 2 }		A:link { color: #0000ff; so-language: zxx }	--></style><h3 style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102);"><span lang="en-US"><b>testodella canzone<br></b></span></h3><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102);"><em><font size="2">sottotitoli incorporati</font><br></em><font style="font-size: 9pt;" size="2"><span lang="it-IT"></span></font></p><br><br><br><meta content="text/html; charset=ISO-8859-1" http-equiv="content-type"><title>Numbers</title><meta http-equiv="CONTENT-TYPE" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><title></title><meta name="GENERATOR" content="LibreOffice 3.5  (Linux)"><style type="text/css"><!--		@page { margin: 2cm }		P { margin-bottom: 0.21cm; direction: ltr; color: #000000; widows: 2; orphans: 2 }		A:link { color: #0000ff; so-language: zxx }	--></style><h3 style="color: rgb(0, 0, 153);"><font face="Trebuchet MS, serif"><font size="4"><b><span style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">FIVE LITTLE MONKEY<br></span></b></font></font></h3><font style="font-family: Verdana; color: rgb(0, 0, 153);" face="Trebuchet MS, serif">È una canzone molto popolare chepiace&nbsp; ai bambini per la sua melodia e per la sua ripetitività.Aiuta loro ad incrementare il lessico&nbsp; (doctor, mum, monkey, jump,head, call, said ) poichè la stessa frase si ripete tante volte,rinforza i numeri fino al 5 ma, soprattutto, fa divertire i bambini chevorranno riascoltarla e cantarla tante volte imparandola a memoria.<br>È bello far qualcosa Just for fun!</font><meta http-equiv="CONTENT-TYPE" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><title></title><meta name="GENERATOR" content="LibreOffice 3.5  (Linux)"><style type="text/css"><!--		@page { margin: 2cm }		P { margin-bottom: 0.21cm; direction: ltr; color: #000000; widows: 2; orphans: 2 }		A:link { color: #0000ff; so-language: zxx }	--></style><meta http-equiv="CONTENT-TYPE" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><title></title><meta name="GENERATOR" content="LibreOffice 3.5  (Linux)"><style type="text/css"><!--		@page { margin: 2cm }		P { margin-bottom: 0.21cm; direction: ltr; color: #000000; widows: 2; orphans: 2 }		A:link { color: #0000ff; so-language: zxx }	--></style><p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><font face="Trebuchet MS, serif"><b>LINK</b></font><meta http-equiv="CONTENT-TYPE" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><title></title><meta name="GENERATOR" content="LibreOffice 3.5  (Linux)"><style type="text/css"><!--		@page { margin: 2cm }		P { margin-bottom: 0.21cm; direction: ltr; color: #000000; widows: 2; orphans: 2 }		A:link { color: #0000ff; so-language: zxx }	--></style></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VAL4w6JvDHc"><font face="Trebuchet MS, serif"><b>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VAL4w6JvDHc</b></font></a></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><br></p><br><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VAL4w6JvDHc" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="315" width="540"></iframe><br><font style="font-family: Verdana; color: rgb(0, 0, 153);" face="Trebuchet MS, serif"><br></font><meta http-equiv="CONTENT-TYPE" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><title></title><meta name="GENERATOR" content="LibreOffice 3.5  (Linux)"><style type="text/css"><!--		@page { margin: 2cm }		P { margin-bottom: 0.21cm; direction: ltr; color: #000000; widows: 2; orphans: 2 }		A:link { color: #0000ff; so-language: zxx }	--></style><h3 style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102);"><span lang="en-US"><b>testodella canzone<br></b></span></h3><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102);"><em><font style="font-size: 9pt;" size="2">Five little monkeys jumping on the bed<br>One fell off and bumped his head<br>Momma called the doctor and the doctor said<br>"No more monkeys jumping on the bed!"<br><br>Four little monkeys jumping on the bed<br>One fell off and bumped his head<br>Momma called the doctor and the doctor said<br>"No more monkeys jumping on the bed!"<br><br>Three little monkeys jumping on the bed<br>One fell off and bumped her head<br>Momma called the doctor and the doctor said<br>"No more monkeys jumping on the bed!"<br><br>Two little monkeys jumping on the bed<br>One fell off and bumped his head<br>Momma called the doctor and the doctor said<br>"No more monkeys jumping on the bed!"<br><br>One little monkey jumping on the bed<br>She fell off and bumped her head<br>Momma called the doctor and the doctor said<br>"No more monkeys jumping on the bed!"</font></em><font style="font-size: 9pt;" size="2"><span lang="it-IT"><br></span></font></p><br><br><br>
